message.raw:
Added support for pedestrian vs. vehicle gates.  Scoring for V1 and V2 is done,
except for clock management.

Configured score output to go to /tmp/vrc_task_[i]/score.log.

Started scoring for V3.  Will need to merge from John's branch where the hose
threading updates are going.
